---
title: log_construction (osaka-blocks)
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> q_init : start
    q_init --> q_set_address : address = Address
    q_set_address --> q_set_topics : topics = Tuple[Hash32, ...]
    q_set_topics --> q_set_data : data = Bytes
    q_set_data --> q_final : freeze(Log)
    q_final --> [*] : done

    note right of q_set_data
        INV: Log is slotted_freezable (immutable after construction)
    end note

    note right of q_set_topics
        INV: topics tuple has at most 4 elements
        (LOG0 through LOG4 opcodes)
    end note
